            <li>Meet government and industry requirements</li>
            <li>See what's inside your software</li>
            <li>Get alerts about new security issues</li>
            <li>Keep track of all your software parts</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3>Quick Setup Required</h3>
            <p>To upload an SBOM, you'll need to create an SBOM component first. This just takes a minute:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> Pick a name for your software (like "my-web-app")
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Write a short description
